[00:14.58]VERSE 1
[00:16.88]A certain man he had two sons
[00:22.70]The younger of them said to his father
[00:28.25]Father, give me the portion of goods that falleth to me
[00:36.23]And he divided unto them his living
[00:43.79]Not many days after the younger son gathered all together
[00:49.89]And took his journey into a far country
[00:56.72]There he wasted his substance with riotous living
[01:04.45]He had spent all that he had
CHORUS
[01:09.95]You must be quick to believe
[01:13.99]Be quick obey
