[01:21.50]You must be quick to hear
[01:23.81]You must be quick to receive
[01:27.69]Be quick to understand
[01:31.06]You must be quick to humble yourself
[01:35.07]Be quick to yield yourself
VERSE 2
[01:51.90]There arose a mighty famine
[01:59.26]And he began to be in want
[02:04.93]And he joined himself to a citizen of that country
[02:12.70]And he sent him into his fields to feed the swine
[02:19.64]And he would have filled his belly
[02:22.90]With the husks that the swine did eat
[02:26.60]And no man gave unto him.
