[03:06.02]VERSE 3
[03:14.53]And when he came to himself he said
[03:21.76]How many hired servants of my father's house
[03:27.62]Have bread enough to eat and bread enough to spare
[03:35.37]And I perish here with hunger!
[03:41.99]I will arise and I will go to my father
[03:48.94]Say, I have sinned against heaven, and before thee
[03:55.12]I am no more worthy to be called thy son
[04:01.80]Make me one of your hired servants
